		<title>Thai police arrested in China for cannabis smuggling after offering courier services</title>
		<link>https://thethaiger.com/news/national/thai-police-captain-held-for-carrying-hidden-cannabis-to-china</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Petch Petpailin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 10:53:32 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Crime News]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Thailand News]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[cannabis]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[China]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Thailand]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://thethaiger.com/?p=1013273</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>Thai police launched a further investigation after a female police captain was arrested in China in January when cannabis was found hidden inside cans of job&#8217;s tears, a tropical plant native to Southeast Asia, she was carrying into the country. Details of the case emerged following the recent arrest of a Thai flight attendant in &#8230;</p>
<p>The story <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/national/thai-police-captain-held-for-carrying-hidden-cannabis-to-china">Thai police arrested in China for cannabis smuggling after offering courier services</a> as seen on <a href="https://thethaiger.com/">Thaiger News</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<figure><img src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T175033.906.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Thai police arrested in China for cannabis smuggling after offering courier services" style="margin-bottom: 15px;" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T175033.906.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T175033.906-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T175033.906-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T175033.906-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T175033.906-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" width="1280" height="720" /><figcaption>Thai police arrested in China for cannabis smuggling after offering courier services<span class="copyright">Legacy</span></figcaption></figure><img decoding="async" width="1280" height="720" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T175033.906.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Thai police arrested in China for cannabis smuggling after offering courier services" style="float:right; margin:0 0 10px 10px;" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T175033.906.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T175033.906-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T175033.906-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T175033.906-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T175033.906-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /><p>Thai police launched a further investigation after a<strong> female police captain</strong> was <strong>arrested</strong> in <strong>China</strong> in January when <strong>cannabis</strong> was found hidden inside cans of job&#8217;s tears, a tropical plant native to Southeast Asia, she was carrying into the country.</p>
<p>Details of the case emerged following the recent <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/thai-flight-attendant-arrested-in-australia-for-heroin-smuggling" target="_blank" rel="noopener">arrest of a Thai flight attendant in Australia</a> in connection with an alleged drug trafficking operation, prompting attention on a similar case involving courier services.</p>
<p>According to the Narcotics Suppression Bureau, the police officer travelled from Suvarnabhumi International Airport to China, where she was detained on arrival. Chinese authorities <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/phuket/belgian-woman-held-in-phuket-cannabis-smuggling-attempt" target="_blank" rel="noopener">discovered cannabis</a> concealed in 30 cans of job&#8217;s tears in her luggage.</p>
<p>Chinese investigators later determined that the officer had been providing shopping courier services, similar to those reportedly offered by the flight attendant arrested in Australia. Authorities said she had planned to visit China on holiday and accepted parcels for additional income.</p>
<figure id="attachment_1013280" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1013280" style="width: 1280px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1013280" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/View-more-by-Alex-P-from-Pexels.jpg" alt="Carrying luggage at airport" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/View-more-by-Alex-P-from-Pexels.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/View-more-by-Alex-P-from-Pexels-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/View-more-by-Alex-P-from-Pexels-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/View-more-by-Alex-P-from-Pexels-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/View-more-by-Alex-P-from-Pexels-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1013280" class="wp-caption-text">Photo by Alex P via Pexels</figcaption></figure>
<p>After a two-month investigation, Chinese authorities concluded that the police captain was deceived by a drug trafficking network rather than knowingly participating in the smuggling operation. She was released and returned to Thailand in March.</p>
<p>Royal Thai Police spokesperson Trairong Phewphan said it remained too early for Thai authorities to determine whether the officer had knowingly taken part in the alleged offence or had been misled.</p>
<p>Trairong said the Royal Thai Police respected the findings of Chinese investigators but would continue its own investigation before reaching a conclusion.</p>
<p>He added that the officer would face appropriate disciplinary and legal action if evidence established that she had committed an offence.</p>
<figure id="attachment_1013281" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1013281" style="width: 1280px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1013281" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/View-more-by-Surat-Sangwato-from-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="Job's tears grains" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/View-more-by-Surat-Sangwato-from-Getty-Images.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/View-more-by-Surat-Sangwato-from-Getty-Images-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/View-more-by-Surat-Sangwato-from-Getty-Images-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/View-more-by-Surat-Sangwato-from-Getty-Images-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/View-more-by-Surat-Sangwato-from-Getty-Images-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1013281" class="wp-caption-text">Photo by Surat Sangwato via Getty Images</figcaption></figure>
<p>In addition to examining the officer&#8217;s role, investigators are working to identify the source of the cannabis and any other people connected to the alleged trafficking operation.</p>
<p>According to Trairong, the police captain is attached to Police General Hospital. He said the hospital has established a committee to conduct a disciplinary inquiry into the matter.</p>
<p>Trairong also warned the public against <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/national/another-thai-flight-attendant-admits-carrying-drugs-to-australia" target="_blank" rel="noopener">accepting shopping courier requests</a> or transporting other people&#8217;s belongings overseas, saying such arrangements could expose travellers to serious legal risks.</p>
<p>The story <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/national/thai-police-captain-held-for-carrying-hidden-cannabis-to-china">Thai police arrested in China for cannabis smuggling after offering courier services</a> as seen on <a href="https://thethaiger.com/">Thaiger News</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
