					<description><![CDATA[<p>In the heart of Bangkok’s bustling music circuit, a new rhythm is taking shape. While beer has long been the default companion for a night of live performances, a new collaboration is challenging that tradition. Polvanera, the renowned organic winery from Puglia, Italy, has announced a long-term partnership with Speakerbox, starting with a special event &#8230;</p>
<p>The story <a href="https://thethaiger.com/hot-news/events/the-night-of-14-speakerbox-polvanera">Where fine wine meets the front row: Polvanera and Speakerbox launch ‘The Night of 14’</a> as seen on <a href="https://thethaiger.com/">Thaiger News</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<figure><img src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Where fine wine meets the front row: Polvanera and Speakerbox launch ‘The Night of 14’" style="margin-bottom: 15px;" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" width="1280" height="720" /><figcaption>Where fine wine meets the front row: Polvanera and Speakerbox launch ‘The Night of 14’<span class="copyright">Legacy</span></figcaption></figure><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1280" height="720" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Where fine wine meets the front row: Polvanera and Speakerbox launch ‘The Night of 14’" style="float:right; margin:0 0 10px 10px;" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In the heart of <a href="https://thethaiger.com/guides/best-of/things-to-do/the-best-concerts-in-bangkok" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bangkok’s bustling music circuit</a>, a new rhythm is taking shape. While beer has long been the default companion for a night of live performances, a new collaboration is challenging that tradition. Polvanera, the renowned organic winery from Puglia, Italy, has announced a long-term partnership with Speakerbox, starting with a special event on July 10.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The initiative is part of a broader project titled &#8220;The Night of 14,&#8221; a series of curated events designed to bring high-quality viticulture into the spaces where music lives—whether it’s the grit of a rock club, the intimacy of a jazz lounge, or the pulse of a techno basement. At the centre of this project is the Polvanera Primitivo 14, an iconic label that has become a symbol of the winery’s identity.</span></p>
<h3><b>A natural resonance</b></h3>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-1013191 size-full" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-1.jpg" alt="Guests enjoying Polvanera wine during a live performance at Speakerbox." width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-1.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-1-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-1-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-1-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">For Polvanera, the connection between wine and music isn’t a marketing angle; it’s a shared philosophy. Both require patience, a respect for the &#8220;terroir&#8221; (or the scene), and an uncompromising commitment to authenticity.</span></p>
<p><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8220;Wine, much like a live performance, is an expression of soul and harmony,&#8221;</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;"> says Filippo Cassano, founder and owner of Polvanera. </span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8220;We have always believed that where there is quality music, there should be a wine that matches that same level of passion. &#8216;The Night of 14&#8217; is our tribute to those who appreciate the unfiltered beauty of a live show. Starting this journey at Speakerbox felt natural, as they share our dedication to artists and the pursuit of something real.&#8221;</span></i></p>
<h3><b>Elevating the venue experience</b></h3>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1013192" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-2.jpg" alt="Where fine wine meets the front row: Polvanera and Speakerbox launch ‘The Night of 14’ | News by Thaiger" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-2.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-2-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-2-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-2-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Speakerbox has earned its reputation as one of Bangkok&#8217;s most authentic music hubs, a place where the curation of the lineup is treated with the utmost respect. For creator and curator Eddie Mellor, adding a sophisticated wine element to the bar’s offerings was the next logical step in evolving the venue’s experience.</span></p>
<p><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8220;Our goal at Speakerbox has always been to provide a platform for great talent and a great experience for our crowd,&#8221;</span></i><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Mellor explains. </span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8220;Partnering with Polvanera allows us to offer something unique. It’s about breaking the stigma that you can’t enjoy a world-class Primitivo while watching a high-energy set. It’s about elevating the night without losing our edge.&#8221;</span></i></p>
<h3><b>The night of 14</b></h3>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-1013193 size-full" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-3.jpg" alt="Audience members savoring wine while enjoying live music at Speakerbox." width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-3.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-3-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-3-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/speakerbox-3-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The event on July 10 will feature a multi-band lineup (check Speakerbox’s official channels for the full roster), providing the perfect backdrop for guests to discover the Primitivo 14. Known for its deep complexity and elegant finish, the &#8220;14&#8221; is a wine that commands attention, much like a headlining act.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">For those who prefer something lighter between sets, the Bianco d’Alessano will also be featured, offering a fresh, mineral-driven alternative that complements the tropical climate of Bangkok.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This collaboration marks the first of many, as &#8220;The Night of 14&#8221; prepares to travel across various venues, proving that whether it’s rock, jazz, or electronic, the perfect soundtrack always sounds better with a perfect glass of wine.</span></p>
<p><strong>Event Details:</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>• Location:</strong> Speakerbox, Bangkok</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>• Date:</strong> July 10 2026</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>• Featuring:</strong> Polvanera Primitivo 14 &amp; Polvanera Bianco d’Alessano</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>• Lineup:</strong> Rattanakosin Breakin Crew, Future Sound of Siam, Aliens on Earth, The Molam Machine</span></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-weight: 400;">• </span>Tickets: <a href="https://speakerboxlive.com/event/siam-sound-voyage-4/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://speakerboxlive.com/event/siam-sound-voyage-4/</a> </strong></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1013194" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/DSF0007.jpg" alt="Where fine wine meets the front row: Polvanera and Speakerbox launch ‘The Night of 14’ | News by Thaiger" width="1800" height="1200" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/DSF0007.jpg 1800w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/DSF0007-300x200.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/DSF0007-820x547.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/DSF0007-768x512.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/DSF0007-1536x1024.jpg 1536w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px" /></p>
<p><i>This article was published thanks to the contribution provided by the European Union regulation no. 2021/2115.</i></p>
<p><em><strong>Press Release</strong></em></p>
