		<category><![CDATA[Thailand]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://thethaiger.com/?p=1013223</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>A foreign man reportedly refused to pay compensation after a jet ski crash and physically assaulted a jet ski operator in Phuket yesterday, July 8. The jet ski operator on Patong Beach, Nattawut Date-iam, reported the incident to Patong Police Station, claiming he sustained serious injuries during the alleged assault. He also submitted video footage, &#8230;</p>
<p>The story <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/phuket/foreign-man-wanted-for-alleged-assault-on-phuket-jet-ski-operator">Foreign family assaults Phuket man after jet ski compensation row</a> as seen on <a href="https://thethaiger.com/">Thaiger News</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<figure><img src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T153515.514.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Foreign family assaults Phuket man after jet ski compensation row" style="margin-bottom: 15px;" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T153515.514.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T153515.514-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T153515.514-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T153515.514-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T153515.514-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" width="1280" height="720" /><figcaption>Foreign family assaults Phuket man after jet ski compensation row<span class="copyright">Legacy</span></figcaption></figure><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1280" height="720" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T153515.514.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Foreign family assaults Phuket man after jet ski compensation row" style="float:right; margin:0 0 10px 10px;" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T153515.514.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T153515.514-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T153515.514-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T153515.514-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-News-Cover-Picture-with-Template-2026-07-08T153515.514-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /><p>A <strong>foreign man</strong> reportedly <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/central-thailand/canadian-man-accused-of-dodging-motorcycle-repair-bill-and-stealing-20000-baht" target="_blank" rel="noopener">refused to pay compensation</a> after a jet ski crash and <strong>physically assaulted</strong> a <strong>jet ski operator</strong> in <strong><a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/phuket" data-internallinksmanager029f6b8e52c="1" title="Phuket">Phuket</a></strong> yesterday, July 8.</p>
<p>The jet ski operator on Patong Beach, Nattawut Date-iam, reported the incident to Patong Police Station, claiming he sustained serious injuries during the alleged assault. He also submitted video footage, photographs and other evidence identifying the foreign suspect to police and local media.</p>
<p>According to Nattawut, the foreign man, his wife and their child rented two jet skis from his stall on Patong Beach. The two jet skis reportedly <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/phuket/foreigner-condemned-for-damaging-rental-motorcycle-in-phuket?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">crashed during the rental period</a>, resulting in damage to both vehicles.</p>
<figure id="attachment_1013239" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1013239" style="width: 1280px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1013239" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-Cover-Picture-2026-07-08T153239.697.jpg" alt="Jet ski compensation dispute leads to physical assault in Phuket" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-Cover-Picture-2026-07-08T153239.697.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-Cover-Picture-2026-07-08T153239.697-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-Cover-Picture-2026-07-08T153239.697-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-Cover-Picture-2026-07-08T153239.697-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-Cover-Picture-2026-07-08T153239.697-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1013239" class="wp-caption-text">Photo via <a href="https://www.amarintv.com/news/crime/551113" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Amarin TV</a></figcaption></figure>
<p>Nattawut said he asked the family to compensate him for the damage, but they refused. He alleged that the family then split up to leave the area, with the woman taking an app-based taxi while the man ran towards Bangla Road.</p>
<p>The operator said he followed the foreigner and again requested compensation. Footage shared with local media showed the confrontation between the pair.</p>
<p>According to Nattawut, the <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/phuket/phuket-district-chief-addresses-viral-altercation-over-rental-motorcycle-dispute?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">foreigner refused to accept responsibility</a> before lifting him and throwing him to the ground. He further alleged that the foreign man repeatedly punched him in the face before fleeing towards Jungceylon shopping centre.</p>
<figure id="attachment_1013240" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1013240" style="width: 1280px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-1013240" src="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-Cover-Picture-2026-07-08T153209.480.jpg" alt="Jet ski operator assaulted by foreign man" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-Cover-Picture-2026-07-08T153209.480.jpg 1280w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-Cover-Picture-2026-07-08T153209.480-300x169.jpg 300w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-Cover-Picture-2026-07-08T153209.480-820x461.jpg 820w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-Cover-Picture-2026-07-08T153209.480-768x432.jpg 768w, https://thethaiger.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Thaiger-Cover-Picture-2026-07-08T153209.480-390x220.jpg 390w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1013240" class="wp-caption-text">Photo via Facebook/ <a href="https://www.facebook.com/reel/1961740067822043" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">แฉยับ ภูเก็ต</a></figcaption></figure>
<p>KhaoSod reported that Nattawut suffered bruising across his body, facial swelling and a fractured cheekbone. He told reporters that he did not retaliate because he wanted the matter to be handled through legal proceedings.</p>
<p>Patong Police Station Superintendent Kornkrit Khankrue said officers are reviewing CCTV footage and collecting evidence to identify and locate the suspect. He added that police would ensure a fair investigation for all parties.</p>
<p>Nattawut called on police to take firm legal action against foreign offenders found to have broken the law, saying consistent enforcement would help restore confidence among tourism operators and workers in Phuket.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=476&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Freel%2F1961740067822043%2F&amp;show_text=false&amp;width=267&amp;t=0" width="267" height="476" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p>
<p>The story <a href="https://thethaiger.com/news/phuket/foreign-man-wanted-for-alleged-assault-on-phuket-jet-ski-operator">Foreign family assaults Phuket man after jet ski compensation row</a> as seen on <a href="https://thethaiger.com/">Thaiger News</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
